product_name: Keen Bidwell Lace-Up Shoes - Men's - 2012 Closeout
long_description: The Keen Bidwell Lace-Up shoes pair plush cushioning with supple leather uppers to deliver lasting support and comfort during long days on your feet. Full-grain leather uppers provide flexible, durable structure. KEEN.CUSH(TM) footbeds contain polyurethane and memory foam to provide ample cushioning and support. Polyurethane midsoles deliver shock absorption and padding for all-day comfort. Nonmarking rubber outsoles on Keen Bidwell Lace shoes supply good all-around traction for daily use. Closeout.
